                     <join result="offenceCrimeDate" targOrder="Y" targets="t18281204-248-off1313 t18281204-248-cd1314"></join>, - of a yard of kerseymere cloth, value 5s., the goods of 
                     
                        <persName id="t18281204-248-victim2153" type="victimName">
                           Isaac 
                           Izard
                        <interp inst="t18281204-248-victim2153" type="surname" value="Izard"></interp>
